snippet.textDisplay:
8 years ago I was in one sided love with a girl named shahida , never had guts to confess her , after 10th exam I was informed by one of my classmate that she is dating someone else and I accepted my fate that she is too good , kind hearted and pure soul and I can't even stand infront of her , so when my classmate told me about her relationship it takes me 10_12 months to digest it, and in last after 8 long years( 4 standard to 11th)  of one side love when I was in 11th I decided that chor yaar uska pehla sa relationship tha   or wasa bhi tu bolta toh bhi naa hi bolti .... 
And this year I see her in a restaurant for 4_5 seconds and all that things are running in my mind. It's hard to love someone who don't even know u like her , one side love is too hard for introverts like me.
